OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773673869
OL,3,CIranian women's football team to
OL,4,Creturn home after five decline
OL,5,CAustralia asylum
OL,7,FThe Iranian women's football team is
OL,8,Fset to return home following days of
OL,9,Funcertainty, after most of the seven
OL,10,Fteam members who sought asylum in
OL,11,FAustralia reversed their decision.
OL,13,FThe team now hopes to leave Malaysia,
OL,14,Fwhere they had been waiting in limbo
OL,15,Fafter travel was arranged by the
OL,16,FIranian embassy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773673869
OL,3,CIranian women's football team to
OL,4,Creturn home after five decline
OL,5,CAustralia asylum
OL,7,FThe Asian Football Confederation (AFC)
OL,8,FGeneral Secretary Windsor John said he
OL,9,Fbelieved their next destination was
OL,10,FOman, but did not know their full
OL,11,Ftravel plans.
OL,13,FSix players and a member of staff
OL,14,Finitially sought asylum in Australia,
OL,15,Fbut four players and the staffer have
OL,16,Fsince rejoined the team in Kuala
OL,17,FLumpur, the latest flying in on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773673869
OL,3,CIranian women's football team to
OL,4,Creturn home after five decline
OL,5,CAustralia asylum
OL,7,FNo reasons have been given for the
OL,8,Fchanges of heart, but Iranians living
OL,9,Fin Australia blame pressures from
OL,10,FTehran.
OL,12,FWindsor said at a news conference
OL,13,Fearlier that his confederation had not
OL,14,Freceived any direct complaints from
OL,15,Fplayers about returning home, despite
OL,16,Fmedia reports that their families in
OL,17,FIran could face retaliation for the
OL,18,Fteam failing to sing their national
OL,19,Fanthem before the opening match.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773673869
OL,3,CIranian women's football team to
OL,4,Creturn home after five decline
OL,5,CAustralia asylum
OL,7,F"We couldn't verify anything. We asked
OL,8,Fthem and they said, 'no, it's ok,'" he
OL,9,Fsaid. "They are actually in high
OL,10,Fspirits... they didn't look afraid."
OL,12,FIranian authorities have welcomed the
OL,13,Fwomen's decisions to reject asylum as
OL,14,Fa victory against Australia and US
OL,15,FPresident Donald Trump.
OL,17,FAustralia's Assistant Immigration
OL,18,FMinister Matt Thistlethwaite described
OL,19,Fthe women's plight in Australia as a
OL,20,F"very complex situation."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773673869
OL,3,CIranian women's football team to
OL,4,Creturn home after five decline
OL,5,CAustralia asylum
OL,7,F"These are deeply personal decisions,
OL,8,Fand the government respects the
OL,9,Fdecisions of those that have chosen to
OL,10,Freturn. And we continue to offer
OL,11,Fsupport to the two that are
OL,12,Fremaining," Thistlethwaite said.
OL,14,FThose who stayed in Australia have
OL,15,Fbeen moved to an undisclosed safe
OL,16,Flocation and are receiving assistance
OL,17,Ffrom the government and the Iranian
OL,18,Fdiaspora community, he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
