PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773673869
OL,3,CIranian women's football team to
OL,4,Creturn home after five decline
OL,5,CAustralia asylum
OL,7,FIran's Tasnim News Agency said the
OL,8,Fplayers who left Australia were
OL,9,F"returning to the warm embrace of
OL,10,Ftheir family and homeland," describing
OL,11,Ftheir return as a failure of what it
OL,12,Fcalled an American-Australian
OL,13,Fpolitical effort.
OL,15,FHow did we get here?
OL,17,FIran's squad arrived in Australia for
OL,18,Fthe tournament shortly before the war
OL,19,Fin the Middle East began on February
OL,20,F28.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773673869
OL,3,CIranian women's football team to
OL,4,Creturn home after five decline
OL,5,CAustralia asylum
OL,7,FConcerns were raised for the safety of
OL,8,Fmembers of the team following their
OL,9,Fdefeat in the tournament after they
OL,10,Fwere labelled traitors by members of
OL,11,Fthe Iranian regime for staying silent
OL,12,Fduring the national anthem at the
OL,13,Fbeginning of their first match last
OL,14,Fweek.
OL,16,FThis led to members of the public and
OL,17,FTrump urging the Australian government
OL,18,Fto support the team amid fears of
OL,19,Freprisals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
