FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773673869
OL,3,CIranian women's football team to
OL,4,Creturn home after five decline
OL,5,CAustralia asylum
OL,7,FThe squad flew from Sydney to Kuala
OL,8,FLumpur on March 10 after being knocked
OL,9,Fout of the Women's Asian Cup in
OL,10,FAustralia, initially leaving behind
OL,11,Fsix players and a support staff member
OL,12,Fwho had accepted protection visas.
OL,14,FBut over the next few days, more
OL,15,Fmembers of the team decided to turn
OL,16,Fdown Australian asylum and joined
OL,17,Ftheir teammates in Kuala Lumpur, with
OL,18,Fit appearing just two were now set on
OL,19,Faccepting asylum.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773673869
OL,3,CIranian women's football team to
OL,4,Creturn home after five decline
OL,5,CAustralia asylum
OL,7,FKylie Moore-Gilbert, a political
OL,8,Fscientist at Sydney's Macquarie
OL,9,FUniversity who spent more than two
OL,10,Fyears in Iranian prisons on spying
OL,11,Fcharges from 2018 to 2020, said
OL,12,F"winning the propaganda war" had
OL,13,Fovershadowed the women's welfare.
OL,15,F"The high stakes made the Iranian
OL,16,Fregime sit up and pay attention and
OL,17,Ftry to force their hand in response,
OL,18,Fin my view," Moore-Gilbert said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
