OL,3,CIranian women's football team to
OL,4,Creturn home after five decline
OL,5,CAustralia asylum
OL,7,F"I do think in this case, had these
OL,8,Fwomen quietly sought asylum without
OL,9,Fthat publicity around them, it's
OL,10,Fpossible that the Islamic Republic
OL,11,Fofficials might have, as they have in
OL,12,Fthe cases of other Iranian sports
OL,13,Fpeople in the past who've defected ...
OL,14,Fsimply allowed that to happen," she
OL,15,Fadded.
